<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ qiè mù nǐ de tóng zài 迦南691</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ qiè mù nǐ de tóng zài, wǒ xiǎng niàn nǐ de tóng zài.
 yī dài guò qù, yī dài yòu lái, nǐ yǒng yuǎn yǔ wǒ tóng zài.
 wǒ xū yào nǐ de tóng zài, wǒ xún qiú nǐ de tóng zài.
 dà hǎi biàn chéng sāng tián sāng tián biàn chéng dà hǎi. nǐ yǒng yuǎn yǔ wǒ tóng zài.
 yǔ wǒ tóng zài yǔ wǒ tóng zài, nǐ de cí ài yǒng bù gèng gǎi.
 yǔ wǒ tóng zài yǔ wǒ tóng zài, wǒ men yī tóng xiàng nǐ jǔ qǐ shǒu lái.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>691</hymn_number>
</song>